This partially works, it will ignore `ItemBase.IsOverriden` but not `Item.IsOverriden`

``` csharp
    public void Override (AutoMapping<ItemBase> mapping) {
        mapping.IgnoreProperty (x => x.IsOverriden);
    }
```

